  "text": "In this subsection, we give a topos quantum theory on sheaves induced by a selection of contexts. This is just a brief summary of Nakayama [CITATION_1] . However, the meaning of ♭ is largely generalized. We adopt the notation of Nakayama [CITATION_2] here and hereafter. That is, the Hilbert space on which a physical system and observables are represented is denoted by H. ",
